{"tid":2055962,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教育界清算正式開始！左派極紅香島中學政治迫害黃絲老師","createTime":"2020-06-08T10:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T11:35:18.000Z","uid":110749,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"03c6a7ef6490a4931c93ce35a331fc5ba144cb50","tid":2055962,"uid":110749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GeQPVEG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGeQPVEG.jpg&h=be213050&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j38xTrn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj38xTrn.jpg&h=4ce8ec2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxCuVEJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcxCuVEJ.jpg&h=152f4410&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxLcTrp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcxLcTrp.jpg&h=7b50e77a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DacTrp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DacTrp.jpg&h=3b6787fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q51vE6q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq51vE6q.jpg&h=e4d1bebe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHiYOZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHiYOZM.jpg&h=7cab6282&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ksp9bc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fksp9bc7.jpg&h=d9fcd773&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBhyCS8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkBhyCS8.jpg&h=88c1dba4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzOYOZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzOYOZP.jpg&h=ba393d07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3oWb8ZT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3oWb8ZT.jpg&h=a6e5b2be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鑒於李筠佩老師於今天發的公開信，本關注組作出以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n1️⃣：老師曾向校方解釋老師認為當中有的誤會，但校方都沒有接納她的解釋，只針對她的政治理念而作出批判，事前亦都沒有任何警告或者意見，令到老師感受到前所未有的白色恐怖，本關注組不能理解為什麼校方可以不接納老師的意見，而政治中立是否代表校方的政治正確。<br />\n<br />\n2️⃣：老師嚴格遵守教育局提出的指引，不將政治帶入校園，而老師亦都沒有違反教育局的指引，老師卻遭到校方的解雇，而當中原因是因為政治立場，校方曾多次向關注組表示不將政治帶入校園的要求，導致多次校園罷課活動未能成功進行，如今不攻自破，試問校方不將政治帶入校園的理解是什麼，希望校方可以向關注組作出解釋。<br />\n<br />\n3️⃣ ：當中老師是因為政治立場與學校相反而被解僱，如果跟學校政治立場相同的話，是否可以橫行霸道，希望校方可以正面回應大眾困惑<br />\n<br />\n4️⃣：學生選擇歌曲考試並非老師選擇，而學校亦都沒有就歌曲「黑名單」，二老師亦都提醒學生需要小心謹慎去選擇歌曲，但校方仍不接納老師的解釋。<br />\n<br />\n本關注組對老師被政治原因解僱，甚至政治打壓，表達無奈及憤慨，希望校方能夠理解本關注組對此事的憤慨及大眾對此事的看法，並認真反思當中校方做錯的決定，本關注組亦希望可以跟校方溝通，之後日子可能會跟校方再次溝通。<br />\n<br />\n香島中學本土關注組"},{"pid":"871813fbace84ee5509a60c03f1ecabd121bdea3","tid":2055962,"uid":197468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03c6a7ef6490a4931c93ce35a331fc5ba144cb50","tid":2055962,"uid":110749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GeQPVEG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGeQPVEG.jpg&h=be213050&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j38xTrn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj38xTrn.jpg&h=4ce8ec2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxCuVEJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcxCuVEJ.jpg&h=152f4410&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxLcTrp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcxLcTrp.jpg&h=7b50e77a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DacTrp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DacTrp.jpg&h=3b6787fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q51vE6q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq51vE6q.jpg&h=e4d1bebe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHiYOZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/